49 "Dehi, mā vivadadhvaḥ śuṣkāya kharāya
50 yā mama viṣṇāti tvacam," prārthayate sma, "na ca
51 māṃsasyābhāvāt yaḥ asti mayi;

52 kim tu satyam mama viṣaye brutam, brutam ke ete
53 dve ātmāne yaḥ tatra tava kāryasādhakau;
54 mā tiṣṭhatha, mama prati na bruyātām!"

58 Tathāpi mama bruhi, deva, yaḥ tvām evam viśoṣayati;
59 mā māṃ kārayāḥ kathanaṃ yāvad aham āścaryeṇa pūrṇo 'smi,
60 duruktaṃ hi bhavati yasya anyā kāma-pūrṇatā asti.

91 Tāvān eva priyataraḥ adhikaṃ ca priyaḥ
92 mama vidhavā me, yām aham atiśayam apriṇam,
93 yāvat sucarite adhikaṃ eka eva asti;

106 Api tu yadi tāḥ nirlaj jāḥ niścitāḥ syuḥ,
107 tasya yat svastyayanam āśu svargaḥ kalpayati,
108 tāḥ samprati eva ruditvā mukham vivṛṇuyur;

127 Tavan mama sahacārī bhaviṣyatīti vaktum icchati
128 yatra bhaviṣyati Beatrice;
129 tatraiva me tena vinā sthātavyam.
